Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:31.82,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.91,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:41.41,Main,Sage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fathom why you would throw \Naway the advantage of a sneak attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.50,Main,Swordmaster,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. Introductions are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.15,Main,Swordmaster,0000,0000,0000,,If you successfully provoke them, \Nthey'll focus all their attacks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.96,Main,Evil priest,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know our \Nsect's secret meeting spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:51.97,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:52.84,Main,Evil priest,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:56.48,Main,Sage,0000,0000,0000,,We know about your evil plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:59.22,Main,Swordsmater,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.47,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:04.73,Main,Evil priest,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That holy sword! I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:08.50,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:15.23,Main,Scout,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:21.54,Main,Scout,0000,0000,0000,,the Hero appeared and defeated \Nall of the Demon Lord's minions!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:25.71,Main,Druid,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the Hero's a cute girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:29.96,Main,Scout,0000,0000,0000,,No fair... I wanna go on an \Nadventure with the Hero, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:31.63,Main,Druid,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:32.42,Main,Scout,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:36.55,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,Just because she's a hero doesn't mean \Nshe could take them all out on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.19,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise we'd be out of a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.81,Main,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so... cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:48.13,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear? \NThe Hero defeated the Demon Lord's—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.81,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.95,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to slay some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.87,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to slay some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.91,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The location is Water Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.04,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The reward is one bag of gold each.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:33.46,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(272,1)}Goblin Slayer in the Water Town
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.46,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you if you want to come or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.37,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:40.17,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had it figured out, \Nbut now I know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:45.01,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't last if I were to continue \Nbeing surprised by your every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.32,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,So, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.01,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:52.74,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,it's not a discussion when \Nthere really aren't any options.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.15,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,But there are options.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.03,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,You're basically only giving us two choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:02.11,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,If we say we aren't going, \Nyou'll just go by yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.20,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.37,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,So she's right. This isn't a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.02,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Still, the fact that Beard-cutter \Nis even mentioning it to us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.80,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,means that he's softened up some, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.07,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I do believe this is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.11,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet, sweet nectar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.96,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.33,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.03,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,There are many goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:36.81,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,The more spellcasters you have, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:42.31,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, very well. We just finished \Ngetting our travel expenses in order,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.82,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:48.58,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're done slaying these goblins, \Nyou'll go on an adventure with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.29,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Does that work for you, Orcbolg?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.41,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:58.20,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,And no waterboarding the goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.78,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Or attacking them with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.38,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Or poisoning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.54,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,No poison, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.03,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.76,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.62,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,He agreed surprisingly easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.53,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:27.99,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.28,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Water Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.92,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:41.58,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the channels, they \Nhave plenty of wares and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:46.09,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What's good to eat around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.42,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:53.88,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Around here, it'd probably be lamb liver \Nstewed with wine, or fried river fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:57.65,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the wheat here is very \Ncoarse, so it makes great batter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:01.81,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you seem rather knowledgeable \Nabout this, Sir Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:05.19,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I know is. When I told them \NI was coming here, they told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.65,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the person from the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.33,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.82,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Temple of Law... \NThis is my first time seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.89,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing, Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:27.80,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.34,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.04,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person who requested \Nthis quest is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.70,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They said we can meet them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:38.31,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Is the client a priest of the Supreme God?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.27,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're the Archbishop \Nof the Supreme God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.39,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.03,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Archbishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.78,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.15,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Sword Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.57,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,The person in charge of the law \Nall across the western frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:05.00,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,The Archbishop beloved by the Supreme God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.85,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, she was one of the adventurers \Nwho defeated the resurrected Demon Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.47,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,A gold-ranked adventurer, \Nthe second-highest rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:15.12,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't a hero from some legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.81,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,She was born of the people \Nand became a legend herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.69,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.48,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,the Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:27.77,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.28,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.66,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... Who do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.70,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I came to slay some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.54,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I beg your pardon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:40.54,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for seeing us. \NIt's an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:44.79,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,A brave warrior and an adorable \Npriestess... And the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:48.65,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,We are fellow members of this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.55,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Though we were not summoned, \Nwe will be happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:55.19,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.55,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.48,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are the goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:05.57,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,It happened about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:10.32,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,We sent one of the acolyte girls on an \Nerrand from the temple late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.96,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,and her corpse was found in \Nan alleyway in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:17.33,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,We received a report saying \Nthat it looked as though
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.12,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,she was sliced apart while still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.30,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Still alive? So it happened right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.08,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.30,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Was any part of her eaten, \Nor was she only killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.35,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.52,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.05,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.88,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,It was truly a terrible incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:40.27,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,I had the city guard increase their patrols, \Nbut these crimes continued to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.05,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Casualties seemingly perpetrated \Nby thieves or slashers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.71,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Violent acts against women...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.23,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Even children were kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:50.01,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,And then an adventurer \Nhappened to see and cut down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.11,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,a small, shadowy figure \Nthat was attacking a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.15,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,That small corpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.57,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.53,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.71,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are more than a few...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:06.01,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,But how did they even get into the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.34,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt they somehow got through the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.83,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they got in underground... \Nor perhaps by the channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.09,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like a lot of casualties \Nif they just wandered in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:20.16,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins dwell underground, do they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.66,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,This town was built on \Ntop of an old settlement,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.81,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,so there are probably some underground ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.09,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If I were them, I would \Njust settle underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.66,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bright creatures, \Nbut they aren't complete fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.46,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,You're always thinking like a goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.56,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:37.95,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't know what they were thinking, \NI wouldn't be able to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:42.09,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,We also concluded that they were underground
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:45.31,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,and sent out a quest for the \Nadventurers in this town, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.67,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.38,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:55.80,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,And that was when I heard the song of the \Nbrave Goblin Slayer from the frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.76,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,What song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.68,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.86,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,There's a song about you, Orcbolg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.78,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of disappointing,\Nhaving actually met you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.14,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:11.60,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't say that. Bards singing songs \Nof brave feats is how these tales survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.86,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they need to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.05,Main,Dwrf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it, Beard-cutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:19.78,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,The more the words of your \Ndeeds spread throughout the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.87,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,the more requests you'll get to slay goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.85,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Kind sirs, I beg of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.88,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Will you save our town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:34.59,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll be able to save it, \Nbut let's kill some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:38.20,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer! Can't you say it a bit nicer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.18,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:42.64,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,It's because it's the truth that you \Nshould be more tactful with your words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:46.94,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Goblin Slayer, shall we \Nhead to the sewers, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.70,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to go in and wipe them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.61,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The underground is huge. \NIt'd be annoying if one got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:55.24,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, no using water, fire, or poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.57,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:01.54,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,But why not just have the city guard or \Nthe troops of this town take care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.38,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit that I do not know \Neverything about this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:07.43,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,but surely this couldn't be \Nout of their jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.79,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:13.57,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Were you told that there was no point in \Nmobilizing the military against mere goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.00,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.47,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't really blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:20.93,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the middle of battling with \Nthe armies of the Demon Lord, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:25.16,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that means goblin slaying \Nis a job for us adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:29.98,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit that human politics and money \Nissues seem rather troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.48,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in that. \NHow can we get down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.43,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.44,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. I do beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:42.51,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your best option \Nis to go down the well
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.03,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,behind this temple, into the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.16,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Is this accurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:51.33,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is an old sketch from \Nwhen this temple was first built.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.46,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,But the water flow indicated \Nhere should be correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.88,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Even if there is erosion or damage, \Nit shouldn't be severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.50,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.23,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You get to navigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.14,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.78,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. We don't have time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.10,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I wouldn't expect \Nyou to be any other way, Orcbolg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.00,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.23,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.44,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,This may seem rude, as I am \Nthe one who requested this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:22.07,Main,Sword maiden,0000,0000,0000,,but are you not frightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:29.70,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Yes, I'm frightened, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.25,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:36.28,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.77,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,That should take care of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:02.40,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.91,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,And done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:11.13,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,To think that there were this many \Ngoblins dwelling underneath the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.58,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's about what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.34,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm not copying him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:20.36,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be a long battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:24.10,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Orcbolg, I don't want \Nto use the goblins' arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.19,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,They're terribly made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.21,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.01,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,They are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.12,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the fifth attack just today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.82,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, who knows how many \Ngoblins are actually down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:39.19,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how long is this going to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:42.56,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. These walls are made of stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.72,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be any \Nsurprise attacks through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.33,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't remind me of \Nsuch a terrible memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:49.41,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:53.62,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,With all the waste down here, you \Nprobably don't need to mask your scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.53,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't remind me of \Nsuch a terrible memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.84,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, long-ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:03.40,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.55,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of water? \NIs it coming from above?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.64,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.35,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,But is rain underground even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.36,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,It must be raining on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:23.50,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure all the water from the canals \Nand sewers flows down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.32,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Beard-cutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:28.28,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be at a disadvantage if \Nour light source is extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:35.43,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:36.83,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Be on your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.83,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.79,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Beard-cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.11,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,A boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:01.56,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,...full of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.19,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,...goblins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.21,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:15.36,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,please protect us, the weak, \Nwith the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.58,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.21,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold this for long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.73,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:26.05,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,What else? The same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:30.13,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:31.64,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.93,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Just leave that to me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:38.35,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,How many spells do you have left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.80,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.40,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Then use Tunnel. Dig a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.65,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to destroy the town above us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.85,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Not up. Dig down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.61,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Dig a hole in the channel \Nand let the water run down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.66,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,But that's going to back up the sewage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.88,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not water, fire, or poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.38,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Think of something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:15:59.25,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold this any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:03.58,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have another transfer \Nscroll like last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.46,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, I would've brought it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.26,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to throw this as \Nsoon as Protection goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.37,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Once I do, use Protection again \Nto strengthen our defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.72,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:15.53,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, Sir Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.94,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,O sickle wings of the velociraptor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.23,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Slice, fly, and hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:26.23,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that might be to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.59,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but if possible, please don't throw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.61,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.07,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Just... a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.29,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We're jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.68,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.89,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Fearsome dragon, \Nbehold your descendant in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.50,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.10,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.51,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They're wearing armor. It's easier \Nto just knock them off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.86,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:10.90,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.36,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,But you know... there sure are a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:20.04,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,An elf's arrows hit their mark, \Neven when their eyes are closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.16,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:24.60,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh. Such an unrefined arrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.67,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.02,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:38.14,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I'll block the attacks from the rear guard, \Nso please continue your attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.85,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.47,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Time to work, you gnomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.77,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Roll bits of sand together, \Nand it shall become rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.90,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Beard-cutter! Scaly! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.15,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.00,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Now... what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.76,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:15.35,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,No, we need to keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:19.31,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. We did cause quite a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:21.78,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,The rain is masking some of the noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.73,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,but the others may have realized we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.15,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.27,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.22,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.62,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for stating the obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.62,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:46.46,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew a swamp dragon would be down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.29,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Swamp dragon... An alligator...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:52.47,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Scaly, isn't that a relative of yours? \NDo something about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:55.04,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I regrettably \Nhave not kept in contact
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.05,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,with my relatives ever \Nsince leaving my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:08.06,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I haven't a \Nrelative who is so violent, Sir Mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.94,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this sure beats walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.95,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Steady your breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.19,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.68,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You have one miracle left, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.79,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you fainting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.80,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's feed the dwarf to that thing and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.81,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely get food poisoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.08,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.31,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming from the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.28,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Another goblin ship... Actually, \Nthere might be a number of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.88,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.36,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.72,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I don't know what you've thought \Nup, but no poison or burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.82,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go with your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:11.04,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,O merciful Earth Mother, please bless us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:13.66,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,the wanderers in the \Ndarkness, with holy light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:17.80,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. You cast Holy Light \Non the swamp dragon's tail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.69,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,and lured out the goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.94,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Since I can't use poison, fire, or water,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.00,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,this was all that was left, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.52,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,But to think they'd be so easily \Nfooled by just some light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:34.92,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They've learned that adventurers \Ntravel around with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.15,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.83,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when they learned it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:40.40,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,but they all seem to know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.45,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, their kind only pillages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:46.87,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They don't think of building \Nanything on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:51.08,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Again, they're not bright creatures, \Nbut they aren't complete fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.33,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They quickly learn how to use various tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.46,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If they're taught how to use boats, \Nthey will quickly catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.58,Main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you knowledgeable?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:01.05,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:06.45,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I won't give them any more ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.82,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slaughter them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:12.83,Main,Dwarf shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... someone showed \Nthem how to use boats?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.73,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:19.48,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,But it's possible a goblin shaman \Ncould have figured it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.02,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:24.96,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,But if they naturally increased \Nin numbers down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.02,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't they... What was that thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.69,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Um... the swamp dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.45,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.55,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins didn't know about that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:37.17,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If they had, they wouldn't \Nhave thought to use boats...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:39.64,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,because they're cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:43.29,Main,Lizardman priest,0000,0000,0000,,What are you suggesting, Sir Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:48.47,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins down there \Ndidn't multiply naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:57.80,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, or something, \Nis artificially causing all this.
